'''密克羅尼西亞翠鳥'''（[[學名|學名]]''Todiramphus cinnamominus''）是[[關島|關島]]、[[波納佩|波納佩]]及[[帛琉|帛琉]]的一種[[翠鳥|翠鳥]]。其下的[[亞種|亞種]][[關島密克羅尼西亞翠鳥|關島密克羅尼西亞翠鳥]]因[[棕樹蛇|棕樹蛇]]的入侵而在野外[[滅絕|滅絕]]，只可以[[飼養繁殖|飼養繁殖]]。

==分類及特徵==
密克羅尼西亞翠鳥有三個[[亞種|亞種]]，每一個限於單一島嶼上：
* [[關島密克羅尼西亞翠鳥|關島密克羅尼西亞翠鳥]]（''T. c. cinnamominus''）：指名亞種。
* [[波納佩密克羅尼西亞翠鳥|波納佩密克羅尼西亞翠鳥]]（''T. c. reichenbachii''）
* [[帛琉密克羅尼西亞翠鳥|帛琉密克羅尼西亞翠鳥]]（''T. c. pelewensis''）

已[[滅絕|滅絕]]的[[琉球翠鳥|琉球翠鳥]]有時也會被分類成密克羅尼西亞翠鳥的亞種。<ref name=Fry1992>{{Cite book en|author=Fry, C.H., K. Fry, A. Harris|year=1992|title=Kingfishers, Bee-eaters, and Rollers|publisher=Princeton University Press|location=Princeton, NJ}}</ref>

這些亞種的分別主要在其[[主羽|主羽]]及體型大小上，[[帛琉|帛琉]]的最為細小，而[[關島|關島]]的則最大。<ref name=Pratt1987>{{Cite book en|author=Pratt, H.D., P.L. Bruner, and D.G. Berrett|year=1987|title=The Birds of Hawaii and the Tropical Pacific|publisher=Princeton University Press|location=Princeton, NJ}}</ref>牠們的色彩鮮艷，長約20-24厘米，體型中等。牠們的背部呈虹藍色，[[頭部|頭部]]呈銹肉桂色。[[波納佩|波納佩]]及帛琉的成鳥下身呈白色，幼鳥的下身卻是肉桂色。相反，關島的雄性成鳥下身卻是肉桂色，而雌鳥及幼鳥的下身是白色。所有亞種的喙都是側面扁平的，腳深色。

==行為==
[[Image:Guam_Micronesian_Kingfisher_at_Bronx_Zoo-8-4c.jpg|thumb]]是[[美國|美國]]其中一個協助飼養繁殖密克羅尼西亞翠鳥的地方。]]
密克羅尼西亞翠鳥是生活在[[森林|森林]]之中，傾向不怎麼露面。在[[波納佩|波納佩]]，牠們會沿森林邊緣在電話線上覓食；在[[帛琉|帛琉]]的則很不明顯。牠們只吃[[甲殼類|甲殼類]]。在[[關島|關島]]，牠們的巢是在軟木樹中挖穴而成或進佔[[白蟻|白蟻]]的<ref name=Marshall1989>{{Cite journal en|author=Marshall, S.D.|year=1989|title=Nest sites of the Micronesian Kingfisher on Guam|journal=Wilson Bulletin|volume=101|pages=472-7}}</ref>；在波納佩，牠們的巢則是進佔白蟻的。<ref name=KeslerHaig2005>{{Cite journal en|author=Kesler, D.C., and S.M. Haig|year=2005|title=Selection of arboreal termitaria for nesting by cooperatively breeding Pohnpei Micronesian Kingfishers|journal=Ibis|volume=147|pages=188-96}}</ref>牠們會保護自己的地盤。<ref name=Kesler2006>{{Cite book en|author=Kesler, D.C.|year=2006|title=Population demography, resource use, and movement in cooperatively breeding Micronesian Kingfishers|publisher=Doctoral dissertation. Oregon State University|location=Corvallis, OR}}</ref>雙親都會照顧雛鳥，一些波納佩的雛鳥會留在雙親身邊較長時間。<ref name=Kesler2002>{{Cite book en|author=Kesler, D.C.|year=2002|title=Nest site selection in cooperatively breeding Pohnpei Micronesian Kingfishers (''Halcyon cinnamomina reichenbachii''): Does nest-site abundance limit reproductive opportunities?|publisher=M.S. thesis. Oregon State University|location=Corvallis, OR}}</ref>

==保育狀況==
兩個密克羅尼西亞翠鳥的[[亞種|亞種]]都面臨生存威脅。[[關島|關島]]的被入侵的[[棕樹蛇|棕樹蛇]]所[[滅絕|滅絕]]<ref name=Savidge1984>{{Cite journal en|author=Savidge, J. A.|year=1987|title=Extinction of an island forest avifauna by an introduced snake|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_ecology_1987-06_68_3/page/660|journal=Ecology|volume=68|pages=660-8}}</ref>，現時已被[[美國|美國]]列為[[瀕危物種|瀕危物種]]。<ref name="U.S. Fish and Wildlife Service1984">U.S. Fish and Wildlife Service, 1984. ''Endangered and threatened wildlife and plants: determination of endangered status for seven birds and two bats on Guam and the Northern Mariana Islands''. Federal Register 50 CFR Part 17 49(167), 33881-33885.</ref>牠們只有飼養的群落，為數少於100隻。現已有計畫將牠們重新引入到關島的保護區及[[森林|森林]]中。<ref name="US Fish and Wildlife Service2004">U.S. Fish and Wildlife Service, 2004. ''Draft Revised Recovery Plan for the Sihek or Guam Micronesian Kingfisher (''Halcyon cinnamomina cinnamomina'')''.</ref>在波納佩的亞種於1983年至1994年間就下降了63%。<ref name=Buden2000>{{Cite journal en|author=Buden, D.W.|year=2000|title=A comparison of 1983 and 1994 bird surveys of Pohnpei, Federated States of Micronesia|journal=Wilson Bulletin|volume=112|pages=403-10}}</ref>波納佩鳥類的下降原因不明。

